sequenceDiagram
    participant GKE as GKE Upgrade Controller
    participant NodeA as Node A (old, cordoned)
    participant NodeB as Node B (new, surge)
    participant PDB as PDB Check
    participant HPA as HPA Check

    GKE->>NodeB: Create surge node (e2-standard-2)
    NodeB-->>GKE: Node Ready
    GKE->>NodeA: Cordon (SchedulingDisabled)
    GKE->>PDB: Can I evict summarizer?
    PDB->>PDB: minAvailable: 1, running: 1
    PDB-->>GKE: BLOCKED (would drop to 0)
    GKE->>HPA: Any new replicas coming?
    HPA->>HPA: CPU 5% < 70% target
    HPA-->>GKE: No scale-up
    Note over GKE,HPA: Stuck. Repeats every 10s.<br/>Node drain timeout eventually.
